-- South Africa's Cosatu Says it Wants Closure of Arms Deal Probe Reversed
-- B y   A n t o n y   S g u a z z i n
-- 2010-10-19T15:14:49Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-19/south-africa-s-cosatu-says-it-wants-closure-of-arms-deal-probe-reversed.html
The Congress of South African Trade
Unions said it wants the closure of a probe into arms dealing in
South Africa reversed.  “Our revolution is in danger,” the Johannesburg-based
labor federation said in an e-mailed statement today. “We
cannot be seen to be back pedalling on the probe into the arms
deal.”  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Antony Sguazzin at 
 asguazzin@bloomberg.net  